      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ON MACI (6) goes very well this trip starting 20 times for 12 wins and five minors. Scored by 8 lengths last time (22.10) in a Free For All over 400m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. CORINTHIAN (3) has been out of the placings last couple but impressed when clocking a 16.76 over 300m at Healesville three starts back. Should be in this for a long way. MR. KIA ORA (1) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Scored by 1.3 lengths last time (22.88) in a Grade 5 over 400m at Geelong. Can feature with the right run. CHAMPAGNE CUDDLE (2) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.",
